1
00:00:21,300 --> 00:00:22,700
♪If not for you♪

2
00:00:22,700 --> 00:00:25,960
♪I wouldn't have wanted
to make a name for myself♪

3
00:00:26,620 --> 00:00:27,940
♪Only when I have your love♪

4
00:00:27,940 --> 00:00:31,310
♪Is my invincibility not in vain♪

5
00:00:31,860 --> 00:00:33,330
♪The towering peaks I've conquered♪

6
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:34,600
♪Leave me♪

7
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:36,670
♪Feeling empty♪

8
00:00:36,670 --> 00:00:39,260
♪I've given everything♪

9
00:00:40,130 --> 00:00:41,210
♪Just to follow you♪

10
00:00:41,210 --> 00:00:43,900
♪Through life and death♪

11
00:00:44,690 --> 00:00:46,500
♪Could it be that love♪

12
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:49,670
♪Is the true end of this life♪

13
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:51,680
♪Why does every battle♪

14
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:54,890
♪Bring deeper pain♪

15
00:00:55,290 --> 00:00:56,990
♪I never got it♪

16
00:00:56,990 --> 00:00:58,420
♪You once promised me♪

17
00:00:58,420 --> 00:01:00,240
♪You'd give me ordinary days♪

18
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:01,620
♪Then I'd rather♪

19
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:05,620
♪Face blades and fall♪

20
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:11,010
♪Into your arms instead of the clouds♪

21
00:01:11,010 --> 00:01:14,210
♪I'll pass through layers of fog♪

22
00:01:14,210 --> 00:01:16,020
♪And barriers♪

23
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:19,410
♪The world's rights and wrongs,
wins and losses♪

24
00:01:19,410 --> 00:01:21,600
♪Who's to weigh their worth♪

25
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:23,060
♪Only love♪

26
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:27,650
♪Gives me a sky as wide as the sea♪

27
00:01:29,380 --> 00:01:36,120
♪I only want to be your hero♪

28
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:41,140
=The Prisoner of Beauty=

29
00:01:51,380 --> 00:01:54,220
=Episode 1=

30
00:01:54,930 --> 00:01:55,850
Grandfather,

31
00:01:56,850 --> 00:01:57,980
what kind

32
00:01:57,980 --> 00:01:59,460
of person is Wei Shao?

33
00:02:00,820 --> 00:02:03,700
You should know his grandfather first.

34
00:02:04,780 --> 00:02:07,090
When I first became
the Governor of Yanzhou,

35
00:02:07,090 --> 00:02:09,820
I held a Deer Hunt,

36
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:12,540
inviting lords

37
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:14,980
of various states

38
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:16,980
to a hunting game.

39
00:02:17,420 --> 00:02:18,700
(Xiaoqiao)
But actually,

40
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:19,860
(Qiao Gui's Granddaughter)

41
00:02:19,860 --> 00:02:21,210
I meant to

42
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:23,140
make allies.

43
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:25,250
We were

44
00:02:26,930 --> 00:02:29,580
like old friends from the start.

45
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:32,620
(Kangjun, Yanzhou)

46
00:02:32,620 --> 00:02:35,460
I can never repay you
for bringing us water

47
00:02:35,740 --> 00:02:37,460
through the canal.

48
00:02:37,660 --> 00:02:39,120
(Qiao Gui, Governor of Yanzhou)
Now,

49
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:41,460
let these antlers be the tokens

50
00:02:41,690 --> 00:02:43,340
(Wei Lun, Lord of Wei)
of our alliance

51
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:44,300
with Yanzhou.

52
00:02:44,970 --> 00:02:45,900
Lord Wei...

53
00:02:46,690 --> 00:02:47,740
From now on,

54
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:49,780
whoever dares to invade Yanzhou

55
00:02:49,780 --> 00:02:51,650
will be Wei's enemy.

56
00:02:52,530 --> 00:02:54,860
The Qiao and Wei Clans

57
00:02:55,780 --> 00:02:56,780
will live and die

58
00:02:58,060 --> 00:02:59,090
together.

59
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:02,140
As will we.

60
00:03:04,930 --> 00:03:06,780
In the following years,

61
00:03:08,020 --> 00:03:10,490
I built the Yongning Canal

62
00:03:10,970 --> 00:03:13,490
(Yongning Canal)
between Panyi and Xindu,

63
00:03:15,020 --> 00:03:16,210
allowing Wei

64
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:18,490
to have water

65
00:03:19,020 --> 00:03:20,580
and us to have protection.

66
00:03:21,490 --> 00:03:23,060
(Panorama)
14 years ago,

67
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:25,070
Bianzhou sent Li Su

68
00:03:25,071 --> 00:03:26,820
(Wei Bao, 1st Grandson)
to invade Wei

69
00:03:26,820 --> 00:03:27,980
(of Wei Lun)
and seize Xindu

70
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:28,820
(14 Years Ago, Xindu, Wei State)

71
00:03:28,820 --> 00:03:30,690
to break our alliance.

72
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:32,060
Grandfather,

73
00:03:32,650 --> 00:03:33,900
the Qiao Clan sent no one.

74
00:03:33,970 --> 00:03:35,530
They must've turned their backs on us!

75
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:39,340
That rat Qiao Gui!

76
00:03:44,970 --> 00:03:46,580
Are you going to drag us

77
00:03:46,580 --> 00:03:48,340
into war for a verbal alliance?

78
00:03:49,860 --> 00:03:50,700
Father,

79
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:53,780
we've offered Wei enough supplies
over the years

80
00:03:53,780 --> 00:03:55,860
for your friendship with their lord.

81
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:56,652
We've promised to

82
00:03:56,653 --> 00:03:57,580
(Qiao Yue)
send troops.

83
00:03:57,580 --> 00:03:58,740
(Qiao Gui's 1st Son)
Withdrawing them is

84
00:03:58,740 --> 00:03:59,960
(Qiao Ping, Qiao Gui's 2nd Son)
betrayal!

85
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,530
We can use a pretext.

86
00:04:02,140 --> 00:04:02,980
Father,

87
00:04:03,180 --> 00:04:04,860
please make a decision immediately.

88
00:04:09,660 --> 00:04:10,940
(Young Xiaoqiao)

89
00:04:10,940 --> 00:04:13,170
Manman just threw moon blocks

90
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:14,610
for divination.

91
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:16,640
This is the will of Heaven.

92
00:04:17,340 --> 00:04:18,210
Withdraw!

93
00:04:18,210 --> 00:04:19,050
Father!

94
00:04:25,340 --> 00:04:26,300
Stop it, Shao.

95
00:04:26,580 --> 00:04:27,580
(Young Wei Shao)

96
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:28,420
Shao,

97
00:04:28,850 --> 00:04:29,690
remember,

98
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:31,730
do not believe anyone.

99
00:04:32,260 --> 00:04:34,050
Grandfather was tricked by the Qiao Clan

100
00:04:34,210 --> 00:04:35,650
and ended up like this.

101
00:04:41,380 --> 00:04:43,090
You're the Wei Clan's only hope.

102
00:04:46,530 --> 00:04:47,530
Brother, promise me

103
00:04:49,970 --> 00:04:51,780
not to shed tears ever again!

104
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:06,740
Father!

105
00:05:13,210 --> 00:05:15,580
This city belongs to Bianzhou now.

106
00:05:15,730 --> 00:05:16,940
It's Chen's.

107
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:22,730
Throw them into the pit

108
00:05:22,730 --> 00:05:24,140
and bury them with the captives.

109
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,070
(Li Su, General of Bianzhou)
Kill all men

110
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:27,380
in Xindu in the next three days!

111
00:05:27,380 --> 00:05:28,220
Yes.

112
00:05:58,260 --> 00:06:00,730
You meant to protect Yanzhou

113
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:02,460
from war, didn't you?

114
00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:06,460
To sacrifice one or all?

115
00:06:07,210 --> 00:06:09,580
It would've been hard
for me to choose, too.

116
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:12,780
Wei Shao and his troops have come

117
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:15,090
to recapture Xindu from Li Su.

118
00:06:15,780 --> 00:06:16,640
At this point,

119
00:06:16,650 --> 00:06:18,700
if we send our troops to assist Li Su,

120
00:06:18,700 --> 00:06:20,140
Wei Shao might not win.

121
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:22,090
But if we do nothing,

122
00:06:22,210 --> 00:06:23,780
and he captures Xindu,

123
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,820
he'll invade Yanzhou next

124
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:26,850
and seize Panyi.

125
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:28,970
What to do then?

126
00:06:29,850 --> 00:06:32,580
The late Lord of Wei's wife,

127
00:06:34,260 --> 00:06:35,530
Lady Xu,

128
00:06:35,620 --> 00:06:38,540
(Lady Xu, Wei Shao's Grandmother)
is far-sighted.

129
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:42,970
I'd like her approval
for a marriage alliance

130
00:06:43,340 --> 00:06:45,460
to bury the hatchet.

131
00:06:47,530 --> 00:06:50,210
Is it to marry my cousin to Wei Shao?

132
00:06:52,730 --> 00:06:54,970
If such a marriage alliance

133
00:06:55,140 --> 00:06:56,340
can resolve hatred,

134
00:06:57,210 --> 00:06:59,140
that'll be the best.

135
00:06:59,850 --> 00:07:01,460
But Wei Shao saw his grandfather,

136
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:03,460
father, and brother being killed.

137
00:07:04,210 --> 00:07:06,170
We have no idea if he bears

138
00:07:06,170 --> 00:07:08,170
grudges against the Qiao Clan.

139
00:07:10,090 --> 00:07:11,050
I wonder

140
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:14,020
what exactly he's like.

141
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:21,220
(Wei Shao, Lord of Wei)

142
00:07:24,820 --> 00:07:28,180
(Kangjun, Yanzhou)

143
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:31,340
Here, toss! Over here!

144
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:32,460
Toss it over!

145
00:07:32,650 --> 00:07:33,850
- Try and hit me, too.
- Here.

146
00:07:33,850 --> 00:07:35,090
Give me that.

147
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:37,290
You hit me!

148
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,290
Hit her!

149
00:07:39,290 --> 00:07:40,410
(Daqiao, Qiao Yue's Daughter)

150
00:07:40,410 --> 00:07:41,340
Good. Over here.

151
00:07:41,340 --> 00:07:42,970
- My turn.
- Hit her. Come on!

152
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:44,820
Stop!

153
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:45,880
Hit me if you can.

154
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:46,820
Toss it to me.

155
00:07:46,820 --> 00:07:48,020
(Bi Zhi, Groom)
Catch it!

156
00:07:48,410 --> 00:07:50,170
Wait. Time-out.

157
00:07:50,210 --> 00:07:51,050
Let me try it.

158
00:07:51,210 --> 00:07:52,050
It's my turn.

159
00:08:01,410 --> 00:08:02,250
Manman.

160
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,910
- Give me that.
- Manman.

161
00:08:07,940 --> 00:08:09,210
Manman,

162
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:11,940
what's been troubling you lately?

163
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:13,700
Can't you tell me about it?

164
00:08:17,090 --> 00:08:17,940
Wei Shao

165
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,580
has had Xindu besieged for days.

166
00:08:20,050 --> 00:08:21,780
I wonder how things are there.

167
00:08:22,020 --> 00:08:23,700
You don't seem worried at all.

168
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,720
Wei Shao's target is Xindu,

169
00:08:25,730 --> 00:08:26,580
not our city.

170
00:08:26,580 --> 00:08:27,650
Why bother to worry?

171
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:30,290
Won't he attack us after seizing Xindu?

172
00:08:30,820 --> 00:08:31,660
Will he?

173
00:08:34,530 --> 00:08:35,940
Bi Zhi, toss it over!

174
00:08:45,020 --> 00:08:46,020
Cousin,

175
00:08:46,780 --> 00:08:48,740
the only way to keep Yanzhou from war

176
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:51,160
is to form a marriage alliance.

177
00:08:52,430 --> 00:08:53,330
In that case,

178
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:56,050
you'll be married to Wei Shao.

179
00:08:56,810 --> 00:08:57,740
Marry me

180
00:08:57,740 --> 00:08:59,020
to Wei Shao?

181
00:08:59,220 --> 00:09:01,140
(Qiao Mansion, Yanzhou)

182
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:02,260
Liangya's heir, Liu Yan,

183
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:03,620
came with one of his uncles.

184
00:09:03,810 --> 00:09:05,180
(Xiaozao)
His father sent an envoy

185
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:06,950
(Xiaoqiao's Maid)
to propose marriage to you.

186
00:09:07,100 --> 00:09:08,220
I'm

187
00:09:08,220 --> 00:09:10,690
the Liangya Royalty's envoy

188
00:09:11,050 --> 00:09:12,930
to propose marriage
with betrothal gifts.

189
00:09:13,290 --> 00:09:15,410
(Liu Shan, Liu Yan's Uncle)
I heard a tale on the way.

190
00:09:15,810 --> 00:09:17,260
I wonder if it was true.

191
00:09:17,260 --> 00:09:18,780
(Liu Yan, Liangya's Heir)
Back then,

192
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:19,740
when Lord Qiao Yue

193
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:21,780
(Lady Ding)
married you, Lady Ding,

194
00:09:22,260 --> 00:09:23,400
(Qiao Yue's Wife)
your dowry

195
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,570
was worth 10,000 taels of gold.

196
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:27,900
It spread for miles on the streets.

197
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:30,980
If our heir is to marry

198
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:32,690
Miss Xiaoqiao,

199
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:33,700
Governor,

200
00:09:34,330 --> 00:09:36,380
will her dowry include a fief?

201
00:09:40,810 --> 00:09:41,650
Uncle...

202
00:09:43,930 --> 00:09:44,770
Young Master,

203
00:09:45,270 --> 00:09:47,170
once Wei Shao seizes Xindu,

204
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,720
Yanzhou will be in danger.

205
00:09:51,260 --> 00:09:52,780
You probably don't know

206
00:09:53,170 --> 00:09:55,090
that my father and Lady Xu

207
00:09:55,090 --> 00:09:57,220
of the Wei Clan of Wei have agreed

208
00:09:58,300 --> 00:10:01,080
to marry my daughter, Daqiao,
to the Lord of Wei.

209
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:04,440
He'll be my son-in-law.

210
00:10:05,050 --> 00:10:07,700
If Young Master Liu
marries my niece, Xiaoqiao,

211
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:11,050
you and the Lord of Wei
will be in-laws, too.

212
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:13,260
How could we be in danger?

213
00:10:16,740 --> 00:10:17,580
Uncle,

214
00:10:18,410 --> 00:10:19,760
I struggled in misery in childhood.

215
00:10:20,170 --> 00:10:22,260
I couldn't have come this far
without you two's help.

216
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:24,500
Cousin Xiaoqiao and I

217
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:26,570
grew up together.

218
00:10:27,450 --> 00:10:28,290
See?

219
00:10:28,460 --> 00:10:29,740
Our heir has always been

220
00:10:30,010 --> 00:10:32,170
grateful and loyal.

221
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:33,860
In this case,

222
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:35,530
how about we

223
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:37,140
set the wedding date today

224
00:10:37,950 --> 00:10:39,780
for these childhood sweethearts?

225
00:10:41,020 --> 00:10:41,860
Here.

226
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,200
I toast you all.

227
00:10:43,690 --> 00:10:46,450
The Liangya Royalty's betrothal gifts

228
00:10:46,530 --> 00:10:47,980
for their heir, Liu Yan,

229
00:10:48,290 --> 00:10:50,290
include a pair of wild geese,

230
00:10:50,450 --> 00:10:51,930
one million coppers,

231
00:10:52,050 --> 00:10:53,260
ten duan of silk,

232
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,930
twelve hu of baijiu,

233
00:10:55,070 --> 00:10:56,740
twelve hu of rice,

234
00:10:56,810 --> 00:10:58,410
twelve hu of proso millet,

235
00:10:58,750 --> 00:10:59,860
two sheepskins,

236
00:11:00,220 --> 00:11:01,890
and a lynx.

237
00:11:07,690 --> 00:11:09,260
Lynx?

238
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:11,870
(Xiaotao, Xiaoqiao's Maid)
It's more like a weasel.

239
00:11:14,900 --> 00:11:15,900
It is a weasel.

240
00:11:21,330 --> 00:11:22,860
You probably don't know

241
00:11:23,020 --> 00:11:25,290
how hard it is to get a lynx.

242
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:28,620
We didn't have time to hunt

243
00:11:28,780 --> 00:11:30,860
while rushing all the way here.

244
00:11:31,260 --> 00:11:32,170
Besides,

245
00:11:32,530 --> 00:11:34,930
don't most families use weasels?

246
00:11:34,930 --> 00:11:36,530
We aren't any family.

247
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:40,580
Yes.

248
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:44,690
Sure.

249
00:11:48,330 --> 00:11:49,260
How's everything, Uncle?

250
00:11:49,290 --> 00:11:51,500
Offering them a weasel is good enough.

251
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:52,930
A lynx is hard to come by.

252
00:11:53,330 --> 00:11:54,170
Manman,

253
00:11:55,100 --> 00:11:56,740
Liu Yan's feelings for you

254
00:11:57,020 --> 00:11:58,900
matter more than such formalities.

255
00:11:59,380 --> 00:12:01,900
You've been bonded since childhood,

256
00:12:04,380 --> 00:12:05,810
unlike your cousin,

257
00:12:07,020 --> 00:12:09,260
who'll be married into a deathtrap.

258
00:12:10,380 --> 00:12:12,540
(Wei Liang, General of Wei)

259
00:12:13,860 --> 00:12:15,580
(Wei Qu, General of Wei)

260
00:12:17,900 --> 00:12:20,100
(Wei Xiao, General of Wei)

261
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:23,420
(Wei Duo, General of Wei)

262
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,280
Guys,

263
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,210
shall we eat or not?

264
00:12:34,220 --> 00:12:35,980
Cut it! I'm starving!

265
00:12:36,290 --> 00:12:37,130
Hurry!

266
00:12:37,330 --> 00:12:38,170
Have a bite.

267
00:12:38,170 --> 00:12:39,290
Add seasoning.

268
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:41,570
Lord, our feet are itchy

269
00:12:41,570 --> 00:12:42,980
when we can't fight.

270
00:12:42,980 --> 00:12:44,300
Xindu is right ahead.

271
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:45,960
Can't we charge into it?

272
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:46,930
Or do you think we can't?

273
00:12:46,930 --> 00:12:48,780
Besiegement is better than attack.

274
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:50,030
The Central Plains always

275
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:50,930
struggle with drought.

276
00:12:51,230 --> 00:12:52,730
Li Su doesn't have enough provisions.

277
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:54,050
We can

278
00:12:54,050 --> 00:12:55,330
seize Xindu without battle.

279
00:12:55,690 --> 00:12:56,530
Be patient.

280
00:12:59,690 --> 00:13:01,330
