Lord.

290
00:13:13,450 --> 00:13:14,500
Lady Xu sent a letter.

291
00:13:14,690 --> 00:13:15,780
What did my grandmother say?

292
00:13:16,260 --> 00:13:17,290
She meant to

293
00:13:17,540 --> 00:13:19,290
marry a girl to you.

294
00:13:19,620 --> 00:13:21,050
I had sworn to my grandfather

295
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:23,210
to kill Li Su and the Qiao Clan.

296
00:13:24,250 --> 00:13:25,530
I won't marry anyone

297
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,670
until I take my revenge.

298
00:13:28,170 --> 00:13:29,010
Yes.

299
00:13:30,420 --> 00:13:31,340
Whisper to me.

300
00:13:31,780 --> 00:13:32,900
Who did Lady Xu pick

301
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:34,060
to marry our lord?

302
00:13:34,140 --> 00:13:35,300
What does she look like?

303
00:13:35,420 --> 00:13:36,700
Let's see it! Come on!

304
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:38,580
Qiao of the Qiao Clan.

305
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:40,500
Qiao of the Qiao Clan?

306
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:43,540
(Mr. Gongsun,)
Calm down.

307
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:44,440
(We can resolve hatred)

308
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:45,780
(by marriage.)
Think about it.

309
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:48,140
After seizing all those cities

310
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:50,500
and getting to Xindu,
our troops need to rest.

311
00:13:50,500 --> 00:13:53,260
Were we sandwiched
by Qiao's and Li Su's troops,

312
00:13:54,300 --> 00:13:56,340
we might be in grave peril.

313
00:13:57,380 --> 00:13:58,460
How dare

314
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:01,580
those traitors push my grandmother!

315
00:14:01,580 --> 00:14:02,740
If I

316
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:04,340
seize Xindu now,

317
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:06,340
she'll have

318
00:14:07,460 --> 00:14:09,580
nothing to worry about, right?

319
00:14:11,540 --> 00:14:12,380
Guys,

320
00:14:13,140 --> 00:14:13,980
move it!

321
00:14:14,220 --> 00:14:15,060
Lord!

322
00:14:15,100 --> 00:14:15,940
Lord!

323
00:14:15,940 --> 00:14:18,300
A reckless raid is likely to fail!

324
00:14:18,900 --> 00:14:20,780
Yah.

325
00:14:25,780 --> 00:14:27,100
(Wei)
Yah.

326
00:14:35,140 --> 00:14:36,380
14 years ago,

327
00:14:37,660 --> 00:14:39,340
the Qiao Clan betrayed our family,

328
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:42,060
causing them to be killed

329
00:14:42,980 --> 00:14:44,660
and Xindu to be captured.

330
00:14:45,380 --> 00:14:46,220
The enemy is

331
00:14:47,340 --> 00:14:48,900
right in front of us.

332
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:51,140
Everyone,

333
00:14:51,700 --> 00:14:52,860
let's go

334
00:14:53,140 --> 00:14:54,340
to kill Li Su

335
00:14:54,620 --> 00:14:55,660
and the Qiao Clan!

336
00:14:55,820 --> 00:14:56,980
Kill Li Su

337
00:14:56,980 --> 00:14:58,060
and the Qiao Clan!

338
00:14:58,100 --> 00:14:59,100
Kill Li Su

339
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:00,220
and the Qiao Clan!

340
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:01,220
Kill Li Su

341
00:15:01,220 --> 00:15:02,340
and the Qiao Clan!

342
00:15:02,340 --> 00:15:03,340
Kill Li Su

343
00:15:03,340 --> 00:15:04,460
and the Qiao Clan!

344
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:05,540
(Xindu)
Kill Li Su

345
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,810
and the Qiao Clan!

346
00:15:06,820 --> 00:15:07,980
Kill Li Su

347
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:09,010
and the Qiao Clan!

348
00:15:09,020 --> 00:15:10,020
Let's go!

349
00:15:22,220 --> 00:15:23,100
Wei Shao, you brat!

350
00:15:23,100 --> 00:15:24,220
I'll kill you!

351
00:15:24,940 --> 00:15:25,780
Yah.

352
00:15:26,820 --> 00:15:27,660
Yah.

353
00:15:34,420 --> 00:15:35,260
Yah.

