00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:41,780
(This scene is required by the plot.
Do not imitate. Be kind to animals.)

355
00:16:12,660 --> 00:16:13,500
Charge!

356
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:23,300
(Xindu)

357
00:16:37,540 --> 00:16:40,540
(Qiao Mansion)

358
00:16:48,660 --> 00:16:49,500
Manman,

359
00:16:50,940 --> 00:16:51,780
don't worry.

360
00:16:53,100 --> 00:16:54,740
Yanzhou is your home.

361
00:16:57,700 --> 00:16:59,100
Once Wei Shao and I marry,

362
00:17:00,140 --> 00:17:01,340
Liangya will treat you

363
00:17:01,340 --> 00:17:02,540
with great respect.

364
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:47,780
Fan.

365
00:17:49,740 --> 00:17:51,220
As much as I hate to marry Wei Shao,

366
00:17:52,700 --> 00:17:54,660
I can't elope with you either.

367
00:18:00,140 --> 00:18:00,980
Bi Zhi,

368
00:18:04,460 --> 00:18:06,180
we'll have to part soon.

369
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:09,900
Wei Shao...

370
00:18:11,620 --> 00:18:13,060
I'll challenge him to a duel

371
00:18:13,460 --> 00:18:15,220
to stop him from marrying you.

372
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:18,220
A mere groom like you

373
00:18:19,100 --> 00:18:20,660
isn't his match.

374
00:18:33,860 --> 00:18:34,700
You're up.

375
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:37,100
I can't sleep.

376
00:18:41,020 --> 00:18:43,180
I have something to discuss with you.

377
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:45,260
What is it?

378
00:18:47,510 --> 00:18:48,680
After the New Year,

379
00:18:49,100 --> 00:18:50,260
Chunniang and I

380
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,580
used our spare time

381
00:18:52,560 --> 00:18:54,260
to sew this wedding gown for you.

382
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:58,300
Now that Wei Shao and I
are engaged in haste,

383
00:18:58,750 --> 00:19:00,460
I'll leave before you.

384
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:03,500
May I

385
00:19:04,150 --> 00:19:06,100
wear this instead?

386
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:17,620
Both of us are getting married.

387
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:20,380
How come

388
00:19:20,380 --> 00:19:21,820
your dowry is more than mine?

389
00:19:25,820 --> 00:19:27,220
I'll tell my mother

390
00:19:27,220 --> 00:19:28,860
to give you more.

391
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:30,310
Or take whatever you like

392
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:31,420
from my dowry.

393
00:19:33,780 --> 00:19:35,740
I'm not competing with you.

394
00:19:36,100 --> 00:19:37,700
It's just that

395
00:19:37,980 --> 00:19:39,820
once we part,

396
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:41,940
we're unlikely to meet again.

397
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:45,140
I'd like to keep something you value

398
00:19:45,140 --> 00:19:46,180
as a memento.

399
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:47,280
Whenever I miss you,

400
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:48,550
I can look at it for comfort.

401
00:19:51,350 --> 00:19:53,540
Don't you want these clothes?

402
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:54,380
Here you go.

403
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:57,220
Anything else?

404
00:19:59,380 --> 00:20:01,180
These are yours, too.

405
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:02,420
Is there more?

406
00:20:04,900 --> 00:20:07,020
I sewed this myself.

407
00:20:07,020 --> 00:20:08,220
I haven't worn it yet.

408
00:20:08,740 --> 00:20:09,580
What else?

409
00:20:10,980 --> 00:20:11,820
I mean,

410
00:20:11,940 --> 00:20:13,020
by giving me

411
00:20:13,170 --> 00:20:15,260
those things you cherish,

412
00:20:15,260 --> 00:20:17,580
you can show how much you love me.

413
00:20:29,620 --> 00:20:31,460
No, not that one.

414
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:40,700
Trust me.

415
00:20:42,420 --> 00:20:43,580
I'll keep

416
00:20:44,420 --> 00:20:45,740
all these safe.

417
00:20:46,780 --> 00:20:48,020
I'll give you

418
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:49,500
whatever you want

419
00:20:51,060 --> 00:20:52,020
as long as

420
00:20:52,020 --> 00:20:53,980
you'll live happily with your husband.

421
00:20:57,460 --> 00:20:58,540
As will you.

422
00:21:02,940 --> 00:21:04,220
Between the two of us,

423
00:21:04,740 --> 00:21:05,740
if you can

424
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:07,660
have a happy marriage,

425
00:21:08,460 --> 00:21:09,420
that'll be enough.

426
00:21:12,820 --> 00:21:14,100
Between the two of us,

427
00:21:15,980 --> 00:21:18,700
if one can have a happy marriage,

428
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:20,540
that'll be enough.

429
00:21:34,620 --> 00:21:35,460
Get changed.

430
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:37,500
I'll take you to a place.

431
00:21:39,420 --> 00:21:40,260
Manman,

432
00:21:40,420 --> 00:21:42,100
- where are we going?
- Hurry!

433
00:21:42,940 --> 00:21:43,860
Manman, what...

434
00:21:43,860 --> 00:21:45,020
what are you doing?

435
00:21:52,220 --> 00:21:53,580
If you truly love him,

436
00:21:54,180 --> 00:21:55,220
then go with him.

437
00:21:59,340 --> 00:22:00,460
I can't.

438
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:01,580
You have to.

439
00:22:02,100 --> 00:22:03,100
If you married Wei Shao,

440
00:22:03,100 --> 00:22:04,300
your life would be ruined.

441
00:22:04,460 --> 00:22:06,020
I'm the Governor's daughter.

442
00:22:06,180 --> 00:22:07,820
I've been supported by our people.

443
00:22:08,340 --> 00:22:10,060
It's time for me to take responsibility.

444
00:22:10,700 --> 00:22:11,860
If I say

445
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:15,220
I'll marry Wei Shao instead,

446
00:22:15,740 --> 00:22:16,740
will you allow it?

447
00:22:16,820 --> 00:22:17,660
You can't!

448
00:22:17,980 --> 00:22:20,140
- He...
- He's the worst. I know.

449
00:22:20,380 --> 00:22:21,340
Listen,

450
00:22:21,740 --> 00:22:23,500
women's marriage can only go two ways.

451
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:25,300
One is yours

452
00:22:25,900 --> 00:22:27,860
to grow old with your love

453
00:22:27,860 --> 00:22:29,660
and lead a normal life.

454
00:22:30,660 --> 00:22:31,780
The other is mine.

455
00:22:32,820 --> 00:22:35,300
I don't need my husband's sweet love

456
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:37,180
but his status and power.

457
00:22:38,900 --> 00:22:40,740
I used to like Young Master Liu,

458
00:22:41,340 --> 00:22:42,660
but now, I realize

459
00:22:43,060 --> 00:22:44,700
he doesn't deserve me.

460
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:47,900
He looks down on Yanzhou

461
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:49,820
and me for fear of Wei Shao.

462
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:51,740
In that case,

463
00:22:51,900 --> 00:22:53,260
why don't I marry Wei Shao

464
00:22:54,780 --> 00:22:56,100
to make the Liu Clan of Liangya

465
00:22:56,100 --> 00:22:57,020
bow to me?

466
00:23:02,940 --> 00:23:04,860
If you didn't hide anything,

467
00:23:05,180 --> 00:23:06,140
you must've given me

468
00:23:06,140 --> 00:23:07,940
all your valuable things.

469
00:23:09,060 --> 00:23:11,260
Your konghou is too heavy.

470
00:23:12,300 --> 00:23:14,260
I took off its strings for you.

471
00:23:14,980 --> 00:23:16,180
You won't blame me, will you?

472
00:23:20,180 --> 00:23:21,060
Manman, you...

473
00:23:23,100 --> 00:23:23,940
Manman!

474
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:32,340
Manman...

475
00:23:35,420 --> 00:23:36,290
Sit tight.

476
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:38,220
I'm helping her elope with you

477
00:23:38,780 --> 00:23:40,700
to keep her from harm's way.

478
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:44,140
But if I find out you mistreat her,

479
00:23:44,140 --> 00:23:45,780
I'll hunt you down for sure.

480
00:23:47,540 --> 00:23:49,740
If you do love her wholeheartedly,

481
00:23:51,460 --> 00:23:52,660
when the time's right,

482
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:56,180
I'll put in a good word to her parents

483
00:23:56,780 --> 00:23:58,220
and help you rise.

484
00:23:59,900 --> 00:24:01,860
Miss, if you need my help in the future,

485
00:24:02,620 --> 00:24:04,220
I, Bi Zhi, will go through fire

486
00:24:04,460 --> 00:24:05,420
and water for you!

487
00:24:13,140 --> 00:24:14,140
Manman!

488
00:24:17,220 --> 00:24:18,380
Set out now

489
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:21,660
before it's too late.

490
00:24:22,140 --> 00:24:22,980
Manman!

491
00:24:23,220 --> 00:24:24,060
Manman!

492
00:24:24,180 --> 00:24:25,020
Bi Zhi.

493
00:24:26,740 --> 00:24:27,580
Manman!

494
00:24:27,740 --> 00:24:28,580
Manman!

495
00:24:37,380 --> 00:24:39,140
She's unsophisticated.

496
00:24:39,460 --> 00:24:41,180
Leaving with Bi Zhi is

497
00:24:41,380 --> 00:24:42,900
much better than

498
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:44,020
marrying the Lord of Wei

499
00:24:44,380 --> 00:24:46,060
only to be torn to pieces.

500
00:24:48,660 --> 00:24:49,580
Miss,

501
00:24:49,780 --> 00:24:51,740
what are you going to do next?

502
00:24:56,220 --> 00:24:57,780
Check the stable again. Go!

503
00:24:57,780 --> 00:24:59,010
- Yes.
- What about her room?

504
00:24:59,020 --> 00:24:59,890
- Not yet.
- My Lady!

505
00:24:59,890 --> 00:25:01,100
- Go now!
- Yes.

506
00:25:01,420 --> 00:25:02,900
Miss Daqiao left a letter.

507
00:25:04,140 --> 00:25:05,100
What happened?

508
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:05,980
Where's she?

509
00:25:06,220 --> 00:25:07,060
Where's she?

510
00:25:07,620 --> 00:25:08,460
Darling.

511
00:25:10,980 --> 00:25:14,220
(Farewell, Mother. Do take care.)

512
00:25:14,380 --> 00:25:15,620
What to do?

513
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:18,540
Without Fan,
who will marry the Lord of Wei?

514
00:25:18,740 --> 00:25:20,420
The Letter of Marriage has been sent.

515
00:25:20,420 --> 00:25:22,340
Lady Xu has given her approval.

516
00:25:22,460 --> 00:25:23,460
If the Lord of Wei

517
00:25:23,460 --> 00:25:25,150
attacks us for the breach,

518
00:25:25,150 --> 00:25:27,140
what... what should we do?

519
00:25:27,140 --> 00:25:28,660
(Zhang Pu, Qiao Yue's Aide)
We'll fight to the end!

520
00:25:29,260 --> 00:25:30,260
Ci,

521
00:25:30,260 --> 00:25:32,220
look at our clansmen.

522
00:25:32,220 --> 00:25:33,780
Can any of them fight?

523
00:25:34,700 --> 00:25:36,700
I suggest

524
00:25:36,980 --> 00:25:38,940
we send Zhang Pu to Xindu

525
00:25:39,350 --> 00:25:41,140
to tell the Lord of Wei the truth

526
00:25:41,460 --> 00:25:42,540
and make an apology.

527
00:25:42,620 --> 00:25:44,780
What? I can't handle

528
00:25:44,780 --> 00:25:47,100
the wrath of the Lord of Wei.

529
00:25:47,100 --> 00:25:47,940
Tell him...

530
00:25:49,300 --> 00:25:51,540
tell him Fan was abducted

531
00:25:51,540 --> 00:25:52,780
on her way to...

532
00:25:53,140 --> 00:25:54,060
the temple!

533
00:25:54,060 --> 00:25:56,220
That's a terrible idea, Lord!

534
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:58,820
Wei's troops are formidable.

535
00:25:58,820 --> 00:26:00,620
I can't go there alone.

536
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:02,730
It's the jaws of death, Lord!

537
00:26:21,420 --> 00:26:23,960
Lord, I have a solution.

538
00:26:24,420 --> 00:26:25,260
Say it.

539
00:26:25,260 --> 00:26:26,620
Now that Miss Daqiao is gone,

540
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:29,340
why not...?

541
00:26:33,740 --> 00:26:34,820
Do you... mean

542
00:26:35,420 --> 00:26:36,900
to marry Manman to him?

543
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:39,260
Brilliant!

544
00:26:39,620 --> 00:26:40,540
- Darling.
- Nonsense!

545
00:26:40,540 --> 00:26:41,580
Are you out of your mind?

546
00:26:41,580 --> 00:26:42,780
Good.

547
00:26:43,060 --> 00:26:45,140
That's perfect.

548
00:26:45,140 --> 00:26:47,100
She and Liu Yan have engaged.

549
00:26:47,100 --> 00:26:49,580
Wei is strong while Liangya is weak.

550
00:26:49,580 --> 00:26:51,380
We can't afford to annoy Wei,

551
00:26:51,380 --> 00:26:53,220
or we'll meet our doom!

552
00:26:53,460 --> 00:26:54,580
Brother,

553
00:26:54,780 --> 00:26:56,300
don't you know Wei Shao?

554
00:26:56,300 --> 00:26:58,180
If we marry Manman to him,

555
00:26:58,180 --> 00:26:59,900
won't we be pushing her off the cliff?

556
00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:01,340
Do you have a better idea?

557
00:27:01,450 --> 00:27:02,340
The priority is

558
00:27:02,340 --> 00:27:04,580
to find Fan and bring her back.

559
00:27:09,820 --> 00:27:11,580
Fate can't be avoided.

560
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:15,380
(Xindu, Wei State)

561
00:27:27,980 --> 00:27:29,900
14 years ago,

562
00:27:30,900 --> 00:27:33,620
I ordered a three-day massacre,

563
00:27:34,100 --> 00:27:37,540
yet you managed to survive.

564
00:27:43,220 --> 00:27:44,620
Are you curious

565
00:27:46,140 --> 00:27:47,980
about how I escaped death?

566
00:28:04,340 --> 00:28:06,140
Back then,

567
00:28:06,780 --> 00:28:08,940
I killed your grandfather, father,

568
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:10,900
and brother.

569
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:15,700
Too bad,

570
00:28:16,380 --> 00:28:18,940
I only have one life.

571
00:28:21,900 --> 00:28:23,260
It's worth it!

572
00:28:23,540 --> 00:28:24,860
Really!

573
00:28:25,820 --> 00:28:27,740
Lord, what should we do with him?

574
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:28,680
Kill him.

575
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:30,380
That's too easy for him.

576
00:28:41,660 --> 00:28:43,260
Throw his pieces into a case.

577
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:22,500
Stop!

578
00:29:22,780 --> 00:29:23,620
Lord,

579
00:29:23,820 --> 00:29:25,340
don't kill him!

580
00:29:25,460 --> 00:29:26,450
Advisor.

581
00:29:31,340 --> 00:29:32,300
Chopped and done.

582
00:29:40,460 --> 00:29:42,660
(People's Wall)

583
00:29:42,660 --> 00:29:44,620
That was reckless, Lord.

584
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:47,220
Everyone knows the feud
between you and him.

585
00:29:47,380 --> 00:29:48,700
If you kept Li Su alive,

586
00:29:48,700 --> 00:29:50,300
you'd gain public support.

587
00:29:51,180 --> 00:29:52,860
What could that do?

588
00:29:54,980 --> 00:29:56,780
Li Su must die.

589
00:29:58,060 --> 00:29:59,740
Although you've seized Xindu,

590
00:30:00,420 --> 00:30:01,860
restoring it

591
00:30:01,860 --> 00:30:03,860
requires people's help.

592
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:06,420
14 years ago,

593
00:30:06,620 --> 00:30:08,060
after the massacre by Li Su,

594
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:09,580
the old and young left

595
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:12,660
built this wall
with their families' belongings

596
00:30:13,300 --> 00:30:14,620
to honor the deceased.

597
00:30:15,900 --> 00:30:17,380
It's been so long.

598
00:30:17,620 --> 00:30:20,380
The war has taken a heavy toll on them.

599
00:30:20,380 --> 00:30:22,420
- A wedding at this time can...
- I know.

600
00:30:23,940 --> 00:30:24,860
You want me

601
00:30:25,500 --> 00:30:27,420
to get married

602
00:30:29,260 --> 00:30:30,660
for the greater good, right?

603
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:31,940
Lord,

604
00:30:32,660 --> 00:30:36,100
our troops have to recuperate now.

605
00:30:36,540 --> 00:30:38,140
No further action shall be taken.

606
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:45,900
I disagree with you.

607
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:48,780
It's better to press on

608
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:52,540
to seize Panyi.

609
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:55,300
Manman,

610
00:30:57,860 --> 00:31:00,540
you grew up under my watch.

611
00:31:01,060 --> 00:31:02,460
With your intelligence,

612
00:31:03,660 --> 00:31:05,180
you may or may not go far,

613
00:31:06,180 --> 00:31:08,580
but you can at least protect yourself.

614
00:31:11,180 --> 00:31:12,100
Grandfather,

615
00:31:13,980 --> 00:31:15,180
I'm thinking

616
00:31:15,940 --> 00:31:18,580
that to make the Lord of Wei

617
00:31:18,580 --> 00:31:19,820
ally himself with us as I wish,

618
00:31:20,580 --> 00:31:21,620
we need to find out

619
00:31:21,620 --> 00:31:23,780
what he wants from me.

620
00:31:25,380 --> 00:31:26,700
Panyi is

621
00:31:26,700 --> 00:31:28,380
the gateway of Yanzhou

622
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:29,860
crisscrossed with rivers.

623
00:31:30,540 --> 00:31:32,660
If Wei Shao means to seize Yanzhou,

624
00:31:32,660 --> 00:31:34,820
Panyi will be his first target.

625
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:37,980
If I offer it as my dowry,

626
00:31:38,500 --> 00:31:40,100
he'll certainly marry me, right?

627
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:53,260
You're smarter than your uncle
and your father.

628
00:31:54,220 --> 00:31:56,220
Too bad, you're a girl.

629
00:31:56,860 --> 00:31:58,340
I can't keep you.

630
00:32:03,660 --> 00:32:04,500
Manman...

631
00:32:14,700 --> 00:32:17,780
Did Heaven mean to bless

632
00:32:17,780 --> 00:32:20,420
or punish the Qiao Clan

633
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:24,420
that it gave a talent like you to us?

634
00:32:35,020 --> 00:32:37,060
What else should I know, Grandfather?

635
00:32:38,820 --> 00:32:39,660
Be good

636
00:32:41,180 --> 00:32:42,020
to him

637
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:43,340
and the Wei Clan,

638
00:32:45,660 --> 00:32:46,540
alright?

639
00:32:54,010 --> 00:32:56,540
The debt I owed 14 years ago

640
00:32:59,460 --> 00:33:02,620
has to be repaid by you.

641
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:35,900
Here's the Seal of Panyi.

642
00:33:36,540 --> 00:33:38,820
Keep it safe.

643
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:46,980
Thank you, Uncle.

644
00:33:50,740 --> 00:33:51,580
Manman,

645
00:33:52,340 --> 00:33:53,380
don't blame me.

646
00:33:54,700 --> 00:33:55,540
I won't.

647
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:16,380
Manman,

648
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:18,780
write to us regularly.

649
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:26,070
♪The sun sets at home♪

650
00:34:26,070 --> 00:34:30,090
♪Lighting up the land♪

651
00:34:31,420 --> 00:34:34,580
♪I travel alone to the moon♪

652
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:39,350
♪Against the stars♪

653
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:43,850
♪Looking back on each step♪

654
00:34:43,850 --> 00:34:48,100
♪I'm coming♪

655
00:34:50,220 --> 00:34:54,540
♪Fate's fickle; the journey's long♪

656
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:59,050
♪Mixed feelings intertwine♪

657
00:34:59,270 --> 00:35:03,370
♪Tearful eyes meet at the sharp edge♪

658
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:06,020
(Qiao)

659
00:35:06,100 --> 00:35:07,960
♪The hardest to quit♪

660
00:35:08,230 --> 00:35:12,600
♪Sacrifice one for a ceasefire♪

661
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:16,860
♪Peace will last♪

662
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:19,500
Water is the softest in the world.

663
00:35:19,660 --> 00:35:21,460
I've been taming it my whole life.

664
00:35:21,460 --> 00:35:24,500
Overcome hardness with softness.

665
00:35:25,580 --> 00:35:26,820
Keep that in mind

666
00:35:27,540 --> 00:35:29,340
and you'll live.

667
00:35:30,620 --> 00:35:32,100
If the lord is

668
00:35:32,100 --> 00:35:35,020
captivated by you,

669
00:35:36,140 --> 00:35:38,740
don't forget to gain

670
00:35:39,420 --> 00:35:42,100
more benefits for Yanzhou.

671
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:56,140
Lord,

672
00:35:56,380 --> 00:35:58,180
the provisions, troops, and horses

673
00:35:58,180 --> 00:35:59,260
in town have been counted

674
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:00,260
and registered.

675
00:36:04,020 --> 00:36:05,140
What about the households?

676
00:36:06,070 --> 00:36:06,940
The locals...

677
00:36:06,940 --> 00:36:08,980
They refused to cooperate.

678
00:36:09,900 --> 00:36:10,740
Why?

679
00:36:10,750 --> 00:36:12,010
They must've been

680
00:36:12,030 --> 00:36:13,860
misled by Li Su's nonsense.

681
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:15,340
Forget it.

682
00:36:16,220 --> 00:36:17,100
It's not important.

683
00:36:18,580 --> 00:36:19,420
That's fine.

684
00:36:19,620 --> 00:36:21,020
They'll come around in a while.

685
00:36:22,140 --> 00:36:22,980
Lord!

686
00:36:24,700 --> 00:36:25,540
Lord,

687
00:36:25,780 --> 00:36:26,860
Qiao's wedding procession is

688
00:36:26,860 --> 00:36:28,060
about to reach the city gate.

689
00:36:30,500 --> 00:36:32,740
(Qiao)

690
00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:43,340
Are you seeking death?

691
00:36:44,260 --> 00:36:45,700
Handing yourself to me on a plate?

692
00:36:45,980 --> 00:36:46,820
My bow!

693
00:36:47,180 --> 00:36:48,020
Lord.

694
00:37:04,860 --> 00:37:06,260
Lord, wait!

695
00:37:06,540 --> 00:37:07,620
Hold on.

696
00:37:08,180 --> 00:37:10,420
The Qiao Clan means to make peace.

697
00:37:10,420 --> 00:37:12,180
Why not go along with them

698
00:37:12,180 --> 00:37:13,340
and marry that girl?

699
00:37:14,140 --> 00:37:16,100
You'll gain Panyi.

700
00:37:29,340 --> 00:37:30,380
Gain Panyi?

701
00:37:30,380 --> 00:37:32,380
Without striking a blow.

702
00:37:32,380 --> 00:37:33,660
It's too good a deal.

703
00:37:34,300 --> 00:37:36,260
Think twice, Lord.

704
00:37:47,700 --> 00:37:49,140
Is her dowry

705
00:37:49,140 --> 00:37:50,180
that generous?

706
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:55,580
(Xindu)

707
00:37:55,580 --> 00:37:57,380
"The waters are too beautiful

708
00:37:57,660 --> 00:37:59,820
thanks to the pretty duo."

709
00:38:00,580 --> 00:38:01,700
The "pretty duo"

710
00:38:02,060 --> 00:38:04,700
refers to Qiao's two girls.

711
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:09,300
(Xindu)

712
00:38:28,140 --> 00:38:29,140
Let them in.

713
00:38:30,780 --> 00:38:31,740
Open the gate!

714
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:42,300
(Xindu)

715
00:38:46,540 --> 00:38:47,580
Tomorrow,

716
00:38:47,580 --> 00:38:49,780
we'll negotiate the marriage
with their envoy.

717
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:52,380
Why not get some rest, Lord?

718
00:38:54,180 --> 00:38:55,460
I asked to see you

719
00:38:55,500 --> 00:38:56,700
for that matter.

720
00:38:58,460 --> 00:39:00,340
Xindu needs rejuvenation.

721
00:39:00,660 --> 00:39:01,900
The priority is

722
00:39:02,060 --> 00:39:03,540
to gather the locals

723
00:39:03,540 --> 00:39:04,940
to rebuild defense works.

724
00:39:05,940 --> 00:39:06,900
This isn't

725
00:39:07,500 --> 00:39:09,380
the time for the marriage.

726
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:14,300
Those two things

727
00:39:14,470 --> 00:39:15,420
aren't contradictory.

728
00:39:18,220 --> 00:39:19,900
Think about it, Lord.

729
00:39:20,940 --> 00:39:22,260
Picture the forces

730
00:39:22,260 --> 00:39:24,220
on the Central Plains as a whole.

731
00:39:24,500 --> 00:39:26,620
Doesn't it look like a deer?

732
00:39:28,820 --> 00:39:29,980
Yanzhou

733
00:39:30,220 --> 00:39:31,540
(Yanzhou)
is the head.

734
00:39:31,540 --> 00:39:33,420
(Wei State)
Wei lies in the stomach.

735
00:39:33,420 --> 00:39:35,060
(Bianzhou)
Bianzhou makes the spine.

736
00:39:35,460 --> 00:39:37,380
And Liangya becomes the hooves.

737
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:38,220
(Liangya)

738
00:39:38,220 --> 00:39:39,770
(Panyi)
Panyi

739
00:39:39,780 --> 00:39:41,220
stands much higher

740
00:39:41,220 --> 00:39:42,740
as the gateway of Yanzhou.

741
00:39:42,740 --> 00:39:44,940
Doesn't it resemble that deer's heart?

742
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:52,020
Yanzhou will

743
00:39:52,460 --> 00:39:54,660
offer us the heart

744
00:39:55,380 --> 00:39:57,020
only if we become allies.

745
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:59,060
That's the price to pay.

746
00:40:02,340 --> 00:40:03,220
If

747
00:40:03,980 --> 00:40:05,420
she hands over Panyi to me,

748
00:40:06,260 --> 00:40:07,100
I won't kill her.

749
00:40:07,660 --> 00:40:09,140
That's the best I can do.

750
00:40:14,140 --> 00:40:16,260
Your name precedes you, Mr. Gongsun.

751
00:40:16,340 --> 00:40:17,500
I admire you.

752
00:40:17,940 --> 00:40:18,940
We've finally met.

753
00:40:18,940 --> 00:40:20,700
You really are one of a kind.

754
00:40:21,180 --> 00:40:22,100
I'm flattered.

755
00:40:22,580 --> 00:40:25,500
I'm not as talented as you, Mr. Zhang.

756
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:27,420
Yanzhou is

757
00:40:27,700 --> 00:40:29,980
indeed a land of talent and bliss.

758
00:40:30,660 --> 00:40:32,060
Panyi of all is

759
00:40:32,180 --> 00:40:34,140
well-known for its waters.

760
00:40:34,980 --> 00:40:37,060
I had a chance to visit it years back.

761
00:40:37,500 --> 00:40:38,980
It's been so long.

762
00:40:39,180 --> 00:40:40,340
I wonder

763
00:40:40,340 --> 00:40:42,020
how it looks now.

764
00:40:42,020 --> 00:40:42,860
You know,

765
00:40:42,960 --> 00:40:44,270
it happens to be part of the dowry

766
00:40:44,270 --> 00:40:45,660
our lord prepared for Miss Xiaoqiao.

767
00:40:45,980 --> 00:40:47,260
After the wedding,

768
00:40:47,260 --> 00:40:49,260
you may come along to visit it again.

769
00:40:49,660 --> 00:40:50,940
That'd be great.

770
00:40:51,300 --> 00:40:52,380
If that's the case,

771
00:40:53,260 --> 00:40:54,900
why not

772
00:40:55,260 --> 00:40:57,140
hold the wedding there?

773
00:41:22,380 --> 00:41:23,460
Well,

774
00:41:23,620 --> 00:41:25,100
Xindu is majestic for its mountains.

775
00:41:25,260 --> 00:41:26,540
Having the wedding here

776
00:41:26,540 --> 00:41:28,660
matches the Lord of Wei's charisma.

777
00:41:29,140 --> 00:41:31,860
Xindu isn't as rich as Panyi.

778
00:41:32,300 --> 00:41:34,620
It was struck by war not long ago.

779
00:41:35,100 --> 00:41:36,780
Everything needs to be rebuilt.

780
00:41:36,780 --> 00:41:39,300
Panyi isn't as well-guarded as Xindu.

781
00:41:39,740 --> 00:41:41,700
This marriage is of great significance.

782
00:41:41,820 --> 00:41:43,220
It can't take any risks.

783
00:41:43,220 --> 00:41:44,660
The climate in Panyi is better.

784
00:41:44,660 --> 00:41:46,100
The temperature in Xindu is better.

785
00:41:46,100 --> 00:41:47,940
Panyi is Miss Xiaoqiao's hometown.

786
00:41:47,940 --> 00:41:49,700
Xindu is the Lord of Wei's territory!

787
00:41:52,460 --> 00:41:53,300
Miss,

788
00:41:53,420 --> 00:41:55,580
why are they arguing over the venue?

789
00:41:57,580 --> 00:41:59,180
Wei requests

790
00:41:59,180 --> 00:42:01,860
that we hand over the Seal of Panyi
before the wedding.

791
00:42:02,340 --> 00:42:05,820
Our request is vice versa.

792
00:42:05,820 --> 00:42:07,060
What if they change their mind

793
00:42:07,060 --> 00:42:08,300
after getting the seal?

794
00:42:08,300 --> 00:42:10,580
That's why we cannot compromise on that.

795
00:42:10,660 --> 00:42:11,500
Go.

796
00:42:14,020 --> 00:42:15,780
Xindu was shadowed by death.

797
00:42:17,340 --> 00:42:18,740
14 years ago,

798
00:42:19,260 --> 00:42:22,020
tens of thousands of people died here.

799
00:42:25,500 --> 00:42:26,860
Say no more.

800
00:42:27,620 --> 00:42:28,860
If Yanzhou

801
00:42:29,380 --> 00:42:30,580
doesn't act in good faith,

802
00:42:33,700 --> 00:42:35,220
you may go back

803
00:42:37,180 --> 00:42:38,740
with the bride.

