♪Leaving only obsessions♪

814
00:44:05,750 --> 00:44:09,150
♪I've wandered in the world♪

815
00:44:09,650 --> 00:44:12,650
♪Yet cannot have it all♪

816
00:44:14,210 --> 00:44:17,480
♪We meet and part in the fires of war♪

817
00:44:17,800 --> 00:44:21,490
♪Embracing,
leaving tender marks of love♪

818
00:44:22,190 --> 00:44:24,120
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

819
00:44:24,660 --> 00:44:29,580
♪How could I ever forget♪

820
00:44:30,160 --> 00:44:32,440
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

821
00:44:32,440 --> 00:44:34,960
♪To spend time with you♪

822
00:44:35,210 --> 00:44:36,570
♪When we grow old♪

823
00:44:36,570 --> 00:44:39,160
♪Nothing will change♪

824
00:44:39,160 --> 00:44:40,760
♪The misty rains never cease♪

825
00:44:40,760 --> 00:44:43,620
♪Falling gently on your brow♪

826
00:44:43,620 --> 00:44:47,610
♪Lingering in my heart♪

827
00:44:47,610 --> 00:44:49,310
♪I would sever fate's ties♪

828
00:44:49,310 --> 00:44:51,730
♪To protect your smiling eyes♪

829
00:44:52,120 --> 00:44:55,990
♪Even if behind me lies a storm♪

830
00:44:55,990 --> 00:44:57,100
♪No matter the trials♪

831
00:44:57,100 --> 00:45:00,320
♪I carry this longing for the journey♪

